data.description: ALERT!!! INSTANT EQUITY!!! SELLER TO PAY $7500 TOWARD RATE BUYDOWN OR CLOSING COST HELP FOR FULL PRICE OFFER! Fall in love with this captivating haven for entertainment, boasting over 2200 sq ft of total living space. Revel in the thoughtful layout of a spacious 3-level split home. Indoors, invite your guests to the welcoming eat-in kitchen, indulge in dining under chandeliered elegance, or unwind by the roaring fireplace in the rec room. This home features 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a 2-car garage, fenced in yard, LVP flooring throughout the living room and dining room and is freshly adorned with new paint.  New carpet in all bedrooms and all toilets are newly replaced. Embrace the seasons as you enjoy endless summer days or cozy autumn evenings on the deck. Conveniently situated near major highways, shopping, and restaurants, this home offers both style and accessibility. This is a must see!
